item.title: You Won't Believe What This Kid Just Made With Craft Paper - An Actual Aeroplane!
item.description: Introduction We all know that craft paper can be used to make some pretty cool things, but what this kid just made with it is truly remarkable From the humble beginnings of just some paper and a few tools, this kid was able to create an actual aeroplane! Background of the Child This child was a budding engineer at heart. He had always been fascinated with planes and had a knack for building things.
